heading: "Family Living at it's best!"
description:
Please email agent to gain VIP access to Essence Realty properties, book in to opens and be kept informed about the progress of this property.

Look no further than this appealing and impressive four bedroom home, in one of Doreen's highly sought after pockets in the estate of Laurimar.

Boasting an open plan living with an additional front and rear living area that gives you the room to relax with a low maintenance landscaped gardens.

Features include:

• Four spacious bedrooms.
• Generous size open plan living plus separate front and rear living areas.
• Master with full ensuite and walk in robe, remaining three bedrooms with built in robes.
• Central light filled kitchen with dishwasher, 40mm stone benches, 900mm upright cooker walk in pantry and an abundance of cupboard space.
• Double car remote garage with internal access and drive through.
• Landscaped front and rear gardens.
• Central heating and evaporative cooling throughout.
• solar panels installed for more efficient electricity usage.
• Large entertaining area.

Within close proximity to schools, Doreen Village shopping precinct and the new Mernda train station, this property is sure to impress.

Style and Space in Perfect Harmony
Three bedroom home with a full ensuite to the master plus family bathroom; two living areas both formal and casual, open plan fully equipped kitchen complete with breakfast bar style dining.
The backyard provides a fully enclosed spacious area featuring a defined outdoor entertaining area, storage shed and a double carport.
In such a convenient location in Rowville - Close to shops, schools, parks and public transport this definitely will not last!
